# Agent pipeline runtime files (change every run — not version controlled)
.agents/feedback.md
.agents/test-tasks.md
.agents/execution-log.md

# Heal-gate baselines: the Generate stage snapshots each freshly-generated spec here so the
# over-heal gate can diff a same-run heal against the pre-heal version. Per-run scratch, not committed.
.agents/heal-baseline/

# Pipeline scratch artifacts (binary / per-cycle debug output — cleared at cycle start)
.playwright-mcp/
/*.png
/*.jpe?g

# NOTE: .agents/archive/ and .agents/pipeline-status.md are intentionally NOT ignored —
# archive/ is the durable QA trail, pipeline-status.md is the at-a-glance current state.
